            <lg xml:id="TK1098">
<l>acaiyiyaṟ kuṇṭāṇṭōr ēeryā ṉōkkap</l>
<l> pacaiyiṉaḷ paiya nakum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When I look, the pitying maid looks in return and smiles gently; and that is a comforting sign for me.</l>
